### TechFlix API - All available endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080


# ==========================================
# VIDEOS
# ==========================================

### Publish a video
POST http://localhost:8080/videos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fileId": "file-id-here",
  "title": "My Video Title",
  "description": "Video description",
  "categoryNames": ["action", "comedy"]
}

###

### Search videos (all query params are optional)
GET http://localhost:8080/videos?page=0&size=10&title=My+Video&categoryName=action&publicationDate=2024-01-01&publicationDateOperation=GREATER_THAN&sort=ASC

###

### Get video by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/videos/{{videoId}}

###

### Update video
PUT http://localhost:8080/videos/{{videoId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "categoryNames": ["drama"]
}

###

### Delete video
DELETE http://localhost:8080/videos/{{videoId}}

###

### Get video recommendations for a user
GET http://localhost:8080/videos/{{userId}}/recommendations


# ==========================================
# VIDEO FILES
# ==========================================

### Upload a video file
POST http://localhost:8080/videos/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="video.mp4"
Content-Type: video/mp4

< ./video.mp4
--boundary--

###

### Play/stream a video
GET http://localhost:8080/videos/play/{{fileId}}
Range: bytes=0-


# ==========================================
# VIDEO STATISTICS
# ==========================================

### Get overall video statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/videos/statistics


# ==========================================
# USERS
# ==========================================

### Create a user
POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###

### List users (paginated)
GET http://localhost:8080/users?page=0&size=10

###

### Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/users/{{userId}}


# ==========================================
# CATEGORIES
# ==========================================

### Create a category
POST http://localhost:8080/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "action"
}

###

### Get category by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/categories/{{categoryId}}


# ==========================================
# BOOKMARKS
# ==========================================

### Create a bookmark (bookmark a video for a user)
POST http://localhost:8080/bookmarks/video/{{videoId}}/user/{{userId}}

###

### Delete a bookmark
DELETE http://localhost:8080/bookmarks/video/{{videoId}}/user/{{userId}}

###

### Get bookmark by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/bookmarks/{{bookmarkId}}

###

### List all bookmarks (paginated)
GET http://localhost:8080/bookmarks?page=0&size=10

